{## Common Card Base
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ##
    Most card layouts should extend from this template or other card layouts.

    i.e.
    (1) {% extends '_components/cards' %}
    (2) {% extends '_components/cards/standard' %}

    The primary reason for extending this template instead of 'cards/base' is to
    automate the inclusion of content-specific overrides.


 ## Content-Specific Overrides
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ##
    By dynamically modifying the inheritance chain of the block while it loads, we
    ensure the proper inclusion of content-specific overrides.

    This changes the inheritance order from something like:

        _components/cards/base/_base.twig
          ↳ _components/cards/_common.twig
            ↳ _components/cards/standard.twig

    To something like:

        _components/cards/base/_base.twig
          ↳ _components/cards/base/faqs.twig   <-- Great Success!!
            ↳ _components/cards/_common.twig
              ↳ _components/cards/standard.twig

    Overrides can be created for various purposes but are commonly used to customize
    card layouts based on Section or EntryType or purpose within a layout.

    Learn more:
    https://twig.symfony.com/doc/3.x/tags/extends.html#dynamic-inheritance
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ##}
{% set path = ["_components/cards/base/_base"] %}
{% set sect = section ??? item.section.handle ??? item.section ??? null %}
{% set type = type ??? item.type.handle ??? item.type ??? null %}
{% set path = sect ? path|merge(["_components/cards/base/#{sect}"]) : path %}
{% set path = type ? path|merge(["_components/cards/base/#{sect}.#{type}"]) : path %}

{## IMPORTANT !!
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ##
    When make changes to the path or card naming conventions, notice that `path` above
    is being populated backwards and then reversed in the {% extends %} tag below.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ##}
{% extends path|reverse %}